			<li>Reason for Visit - required</li>
		</ul>
		<li>
			 As one of the practicing veterinary doctors, I should be able to record the following information about a customer's pet.
		</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Name of Pet - required, no more than 35 characters</li>
			<li>Type of Pet - must be a dog, cat, or bird</li>
			<li>Breed - required, no more than 35 characters</li>
			<li>Age - required</li>
			<li>Weight - required</li>
			<li>Date of Last Visit - required</li>
		</ul>
		<li>
			 As a customer, I should be able to see when my pet is scheduled for their next appointment
		</li>
		<ul>
			<li>Pet's Name</li>
			<li>Date of Next Appointment</li>
			<li>Reason for Visit</li>
		</ul>
	</ol>
